Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.68,0:00:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜猜誰馬上就要去\N{\fs38}Guess who's going on a get-away to the most
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.31,0:00:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 世界上最浪漫的地方了  - 去斐濟嗎\N{\fs38}- romantic place ever? - Fiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.84,0:00:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夢終于成真了\N{\fs38}We're finally doing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.53,0:00:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去和海龜一起游泳了\N{\fs38}I'm gonna get to swim with a sea turtle!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.24,0:00:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道什么和去斐濟游泳一樣棒嗎\N{\fs38}You know what's kinda like swimming in Fiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.94,0:00:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去新澤西打高爾夫\N{\fs38}Golfing in New Jersey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.78,0:00:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以在YouTube上看海龜視頻\N{\fs38}But we can look at sea turtles on YouTube.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.24,0:00:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我每個周末都看\N{\fs38}I do that every weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.22,0:00:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不一樣的\N{\fs38}That's not the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.47,0:00:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 親愛的 這可是CNBC的慈善高爾夫球賽\N{\fs38}Come on, honey. CNBC charity golf event.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.51,0:00:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 對我來說都很無聊\N{\fs38}Ugh, those things are so boring for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.31,0:00:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被拉去各種合照\N{\fs38}You always end up getting pulled into a million photo-ups
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.75,0:00:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就要整個周末都對他們微笑 鼓掌\N{\fs38}and I spend the weekend politely golf clapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.51,0:00:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我鼓掌很用力的 你娶我的時候就知道了\N{\fs38}I clap big, Mike. You knew that when you married me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.75,0:00:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不喜歡他們的殷勤\N{\fs38}I just don't like all the attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.23,0:00:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 哦 真的嗎 Mike  - 好吧 也許我很享受 但是\N{\fs38}- Oh, yeah, really, Mike? - Well, maybe I do, but,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.25,0:00:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是重點\N{\fs38}this isn't about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.38,0:00:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次活動舉辦地是沿岸莊園\N{\fs38}The event's being held at the Shore Side Manor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.63,0:00:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 有點意思\N{\fs38}Uh, game changer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.15,0:00:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿岸莊園是二十年前Mike向我求婚的地方\N{\fs38}Shore Side Manor is where Mike proposed to me 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.35,0:00:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候我們沒幾個錢\N{\fs38}We were pretty broke back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.56,0:00:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能住在最差的房間里\N{\fs38}so we had to stay in the worst room in the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.08,0:00:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,號稱有花園景觀 但是我們唯一觀到的\N{\fs38}They call it garden view, but the only thing we viewed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.48,0:00:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是一群打高爾夫的人在隨地小便\N{\fs38}was a bunch of golfers peeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正好在前九個球洞和后九個球洞之間\N{\fs38}We were right between the front nine and the back nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.92,0:00:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還真看到一個人的乳溝了(諧音前九洞)\N{\fs38}I actually saw a guy's front line.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.59,0:00:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我們去住那的海景套房\N{\fs38}This time we're going to an ocean view suite.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.13,0:01:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去打幾桿球\N{\fs38}And I'll hit a few golf balls,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.18,0:01:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就是我們的浪漫時間了\N{\fs38}and the rest of the time will be nothing but romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.64,0:01:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 說好了哦  - 我要做你愛的海龜\N{\fs38}- You promise. - I'll be your seaturtle of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.05,0:01:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把浪漫之蛋埋到沙子里\N{\fs38}and we will bury our eggs of romance in the sand,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.39,0:01:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說了 抱一下\N{\fs38}Forget it, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.50,0:01:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 你們注意一點好嗎\N{\fs38}Oh! You people are machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.75,0:01:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個家里就沒有一個房間\N{\fs38}Can't there be one room in this house
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.77,0:01:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沒有人在接吻的嗎\N{\fs38}where people are not kissing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.51,0:01:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊 你的房間\N{\fs38}Yeah, that'd be your room, Ian.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 Mike 別這樣\N{\fs38}Oh, Mike. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.88,0:01:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在Ian的房間里親熱過很多次的\N{\fs38}You know we've made out plenty of times in Ian's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.60,0:01:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 媽媽 我們的麥片吃完了  - 噓\N{\fs38}- Mom, we're out of cereal! - Shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.93,0:01:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽正在度假呢\N{\fs38}Mom's on vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.26,0:01:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躺在一張舒服的吊床上\N{\fs38}Right now I'm easing into a hammock,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.59,0:01:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放松\N{\fs38}I'm relaxed--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.94,0:01:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎么都不用杯托\N{\fs38}are none of you using your coaster?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得先把你送走\N{\fs38}Oh, boy, we gotta get you out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.43,0:01:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Felix不來約會了\N{\fs38}Well, Felix canceled on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.95,0:01:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很確定 我們完了\N{\fs38}I'm pretty sure it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.07,0:01:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧 你那么喜歡他\N{\fs38}Oh, no. You liked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.94,0:01:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他從來沒想盜用你的身份\N{\fs38}He never tried to steal your identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.94,0:01:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs36}身份盜用是通過在線網站等方式進行約會的常見騙局
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.47,0:01:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真的是如意郎君\N{\fs38}He was a real catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.44,0:01:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經做好心理準備了\N{\fs38}I had this whole spread prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.57,0:02:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜這又是一個和往常一樣的周六夜晚了\N{\fs38}Guess it's just another Saturday night
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.27,0:02:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老姑姑Leigh百無聊賴的打發時間\N{\fs38}with nothing to do for Old Aunt Leigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.48,0:02:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還得照看Graham 你不會忘了吧\N{\fs38}Except babysit Graham, or have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.33,0:02:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michael 你說什么呢\N{\fs38}Michael, what are you implying?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.55,0:02:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能忘掉我的寶貝侄子\N{\fs38}I could never forget my baby nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全忘記了\N{\fs38}I totally forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.59,0:02:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你餓了 寶貝\N{\fs38}Hope you're hungry, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.08,0:02:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了一頓大餐\N{\fs38}I made a big dinner that was in no way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.39,0:02:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不是受到<愛你九周半>的影響\N{\fs38}inspired by 9 1/2 Weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.80,0:02:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 爸爸\N{\fs38}Bye, dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.44,0:02:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我和媽媽要出發了\N{\fs38}Okay, kiddos. We gotta boogie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.19,0:02:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里是你們的天下了\N{\fs38}The place is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.90,0:02:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走了 不要玩得太瘋哦\N{\fs38}Don't have too much fun without us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.09,0:02:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 愛你 再見  - 放心吧\N{\fs38}- Love you. Bye. - We won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.85,0:02:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會想你們的\N{\fs38}We'll miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.07,0:02:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些笨蛋 真是好騙\N{\fs38}Those trusting fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周末我們把房子租給別人了\N{\fs38}We rented out the apartment for the weekend
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.51,0:02:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們是天才\N{\fs38}'cause we're geniuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.82,0:02:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以在網上賺到一大筆錢\N{\fs38}You can make a killing online
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.40,0:02:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出租曼哈頓一套四臥兩浴的公寓\N{\fs38}for a four-bedroom, two-bath in Manhattan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 狗關起來  - 搞定\N{\fs38}- Dog in the kennel? - Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 換床單  - 搞定 \N{\fs38}- Sheets changed? - Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.73,0:02:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枕邊薄荷糖\N{\fs38}Mints on the pillow?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.71,0:02:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣有度假酒店的感覺嘛\N{\fs38}For that resort feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 也許會留些小費呢\N{\fs38}Ooh, maybe they'll leave a tip.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.03,0:02:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再回到這里真是太棒了\N{\fs38}It feels so good to be back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.25,0:02:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 要死 我把比基尼落在車上了\N{\fs38}Oh, damn, I left my bikini in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.24,0:02:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Annie 外面才13度\N{\fs38}Annie, it's 56 degrees outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在泳池邊躺躺\N{\fs38}Hey, I am laying by that pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 這也不行嗎  - Henry先生\N{\fs38}- You let me have this. - Mr. Henry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以和你照張相嗎\N{\fs38}Mind if we take a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:02:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你是我們的人生楷模  - 哦 謝謝\N{\fs38}- You're a real inspiration to us. - Oh, thanks, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.17,0:03:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 不過我和我妻子在一塊呢  - 不 沒關系  \N{\fs38}- But I'm kind of with my wife. - No, no, no, no, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和大家聊聊\N{\fs38}You greet your public,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去拿我的泳衣\N{\fs38}and I will go and get my swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 把我舉起來 我躺在你們胳膊上\N{\fs38}Okay, well, lift me up. I'll lie across your arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再用我的相機來一張\N{\fs38}Get one on my camera too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.47,0:03:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝您愉快\N{\fs38}Enjoy your stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗨 你好  - 歡迎\N{\fs38}- Hey, how are you? - Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 謝謝\N{\fs38}- Thanks. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 我正排著隊呢\N{\fs38}Uh, I was in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 沒看見你\N{\fs38}Oh, I'm sorry. I didn't see you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.78,0:03:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我雖然不高 但也沒有矮到你看不見的地步吧\N{\fs38}Well, I know I'm short, but I'm not that short.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 不 我沒看見你是因為 我是盲人\N{\fs38}Uh, no, I didn't see you because I'm blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.74,0:03:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登記入住 這是我的身份證\N{\fs38}Just checking in. Here's my ID.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉沒注意到你是盲人 但是\N{\fs38}Well, I'm sorry I didn't notice you were blind, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 但是 但是 但是什么\N{\fs38}But-- but-- but-- but-- but-- but what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你還是排到我前面去了\N{\fs38}But you're still in front of me in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我瞎得不知道我在你前面嗎\N{\fs38}Oh, because I'm blind I don't know where I am in line?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你當然知道 只是\N{\fs38}No, you totally do. It's just that--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.06,0:03:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 別說了\N{\fs38}You know what, hold that thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 快點搞定吧  - 好了\N{\fs38}- Just let me finish.  - Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝\N{\fs38}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 無論如何\N{\fs38}Now, by all means.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}Vernon\NVernon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 無所謂\N{\fs38}Well, as long as you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 登記入住 我是Mike Henry\N{\fs38}Hi, checking in. Mike Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:03:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 你將入住我們的園景套房\N{\fs38}Great, we've got you in a garden view suite.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不\N{\fs38}Oh, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們想要的是海景套房\N{\fs38}We were expecting an ocean view suite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊\N{\fs38}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那位先生要了最后一間了\N{\fs38}That gentleman just got the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.56,0:04:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎\N{\fs38}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.55,0:04:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去是有點浪費了啊\N{\fs38}Kind of seems like a waste of an ocean view suite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為\N{\fs38}Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.99,0:04:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂的\N{\fs38}I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.39,0:04:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的鑰匙\N{\fs38}Here's your key.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚是我的第三次約會 可是在最后一分鐘\N{\fs38}I had a third date tonight, but the guy canceled
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.44,0:04:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個家伙不來了\N{\fs38}at the last minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.05,0:04:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前景堪憂啊\N{\fs38}Not a good sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.19,0:04:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么\N{\fs38}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.22,0:04:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三次約會是這樣的\N{\fs38}Third date's make or break--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.73,0:04:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帶他回家 喂點吃的\N{\fs38}You take him home, feed him some figs,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后他凝視著你的眼睛\N{\fs38}then he looks into your eyes and says
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說出你期待很久的那三個字\N{\fs38}those three words you've been longing to hear--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"我離了"\N{\fs38}"I'm getting divorced."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我朋友Tommy的爸爸媽媽也離婚了\N{\fs38}My friend Tommy's parents are divorced.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.99,0:04:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢\N{\fs38}Good story.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來老姑姑Leigh\N{\fs38}Yep, I guess Old Aunt Leigh's
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注定和約會無緣了\N{\fs38}just destined to be dateless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來和你約會\N{\fs38}I'll be your date.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.88,0:04:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢\N{\fs38}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是紳士\N{\fs38}Such a gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么你頭頂\N{\fs38}Why is your hair a different color
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:04:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭發的顏色不一樣\N{\fs38}on the top of your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:05:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紳士是不問問題的 Graham\N{\fs38}Gentlemen don't ask questions, Graham.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Annie 你不冷嗎\N{\fs38}- - Annie, you must be freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神大于肉體 我要保持鮮活的度假之心\N{\fs38}Mind over matter-- Needed to keep the vacation spirit alive
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們沒能訂到海景套房\N{\fs38}since we didn't get the ocean view suite.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.04,0:05:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好消息是\N{\fs38}Oh, good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.88,0:05:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我預約了情侶按摩\N{\fs38}I booked us a couples massage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就不去晚宴了吧\N{\fs38}So I figured we could skip the banquet,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吃一頓安靜浪漫的二人晚餐\N{\fs38}have a quiet, romantic dinner for two.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在室內 對吧\N{\fs38}Oh, that's inside, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的腳趾已經沒有知覺了\N{\fs38}Because I can't really feel my toes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗨 Mike  - 嗨 Harris\N{\fs38}- Hey, Mike.  - Hey, Harris.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重返球場了啊 嘿 Annie\N{\fs38}Back in the game. Hey, Annie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 套件羊毛衫  - 我知道\N{\fs38}- Throw on a fleece. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.81,0:05:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好去給圣阿比蓋爾醫院\N{\fs38}So ready to get out there and raise some funds
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.77,0:05:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籌款了嗎\N{\fs38}for St. Abigail's Hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.91,0:05:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望是準備好了 \N{\fs38}I hope the answer's yes because those nuns
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些修女盯我可盯得很緊\N{\fs38}are breathing down my neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.81,0:05:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Harris 見我笑 錢包開\N{\fs38}Harris, this smile opens wallets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.49,0:05:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著\N{\fs38}Watch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 都注意好躲開\N{\fs38}Okay, get ready to duck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在后面的也不安全哦\N{\fs38}And don't think you're safe back there either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇\N{\fs38}Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我老公\N{\fs38}- That's my husband. -
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.51,0:05:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰要在這么漂亮的一桿后面打可慘了啊\N{\fs38}Hate to be the guy who has to follow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.48,0:05:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說 是誰要和我一起打\N{\fs38}Who am I partnered with anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.98,0:05:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個叫Chaz Garrity的\N{\fs38}Oh, just a little someone by the name of Chaz Garrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.97,0:05:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爵士音樂家\N{\fs38}The jazz musician.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.03,0:05:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在肯尼迪中心表演過\N{\fs38}He played the Kennedy Center.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.03,0:05:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五點檔新聞的主題曲就是他寫的 \N{\fs38}He wrote the theme for our 5:00 News, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:06:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 噢 我喜歡那段  - 是啊\N{\fs38}- Oh, I love that. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高爾夫也打得很好\N{\fs38}Hell of a golfer too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.77,0:06:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點尤其厲害\N{\fs38}Which is amazing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.41,0:06:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考慮到他的個人因素\N{\fs38}considering his personal challenges.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在哪兒\N{\fs38}There he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 那人  - 沒錯\N{\fs38}- That guy? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在籌款 Mike 各個社會名流都來幫忙了\N{\fs38}I'm raising funds here, Mike. Every celebrity helps.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們回到了1961年\N{\fs38}So it's 1961,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爵士音樂家又成了社會名流了嗎\N{\fs38}and jazz musicians are celebrities again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爵士是唯一純粹的美國藝術\N{\fs38}Hey, jazz is the only pure American art form.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去打個招呼把\N{\fs38}Now go over there and say hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.22,0:06:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行\N{\fs38}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.99,0:06:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 Chaz\N{\fs38}Hey, Chaz.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.73,0:06:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么樣 我們今天一起打球\N{\fs38}How you doing? I guess we're partners today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.71,0:06:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺出人意料的 是吧\N{\fs38}This is kind of surprising, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.04,0:06:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出人意料 怎么 因為我是盲人嗎 \N{\fs38}"Surprising"? Why, 'cause I'm blind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 因為我們之前遇見過\N{\fs38}Well, no, no. But because we met earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我有帕金森\N{\fs38}And-- and, you know, I have Parkinson's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.76,0:06:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能理解克服個人\N{\fs38}So I know something about overcoming personal--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,障礙\N{\fs38}Obstacles?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你想說這個嗎  - 障礙 是的\N{\fs38}- Is that what you were gonna say? - Obstacles, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 我可不想被拖進\N{\fs38}Listen, I don't want to get dragged down
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那悲慘 消極的世界 \N{\fs38}into your sad, negative world, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來玩的\N{\fs38}I'm just here to play a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲慘\N{\fs38}- - "Sad"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得了吧\N{\fs38}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇\N{\fs38}Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇哦\N{\fs38}Oh, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽上去不錯\N{\fs38}That sounded good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打了多遠 我看不見\N{\fs38}Hey, how far did that go? I couldn't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球\N{\fs38}Nice shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇\N{\fs38}Yes! Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽吶\N{\fs38}Listen to that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽上去會是小鳥球啊\N{\fs38}Sounds like a birdie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs36}小鳥球 指高爾夫中低于標準桿一桿的成績
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情侶按摩時間\N{\fs38}Couples massage time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好在另一個男人摸我的時候跟我眉來眼去了嗎\N{\fs38}You ready to make eye contact while another guy touches me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的 我得把這場打完\N{\fs38}Oh, honey. I-I gotta finish this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這Chaz在跟我較勁兒\N{\fs38}This Chaz guy called me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.09,0:07:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"跟你較勁兒" 你還是16歲么\N{\fs38}"Called you out"? What, are you 16?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.53,0:07:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要在寡婦彎道跟他一較高下\N{\fs38}You gonna drag race him down widow's curve?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.53,0:07:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs36}Widow's Curve 極度危險的彎道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然不 親愛的 他是盲人 不能開車\N{\fs38}Of course not, honey. He's blind. He can't drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.62,0:07:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為這周末\N{\fs38}I thought this weekend
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只打幾個球\N{\fs38}you were just gonna hit a few balls
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.49,0:07:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的時間都是屬于我倆的\N{\fs38}and the rest of the time was gonna be about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.39,0:07:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你能理解\N{\fs38}Thanks for understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很難做到嗎 當然\N{\fs38}Is it hard? Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我練成了這雙手\N{\fs38}But I've trained my hands to have sight
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能見雙眼所不見\N{\fs38}where my eyes don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便一提 你的微笑很美 \N{\fs38}Beautiful smile, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.88,0:07:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把電話給這個人\N{\fs38}Give this guy your number.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.82,0:08:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Chaz  - 干嘛\N{\fs38}- Chaz. - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.32,0:08:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能給你提個醒嗎\N{\fs38}Can I give you a little tip
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個勵志人物給另一個提的醒\N{\fs38}from one inspirational guy to another?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都知道你是盲人\N{\fs38}Everybody knows you're blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.48,0:08:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什么\N{\fs38}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你有些在利用這一點\N{\fs38}You're just-- you're milking it a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我在  - 只是一點\N{\fs38}- I'm-- - Just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.16,0:08:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在利用這點\N{\fs38}I'm milking it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒說\N{\fs38}Okay, I wasn't the one who said,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.96,0:08:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"我有帕金森 這是種障礙"\N{\fs38}"I have Parkinson's. It's an obstacle."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.15,0:08:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今天你在大廳里呢\N{\fs38}Oh, how about you in the lobby today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是盲人 我是盲人\N{\fs38}"I'm blind. I'm blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要風景好的房間 我是盲人\N{\fs38}Give me a room with a view! I'm blind!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.57,0:08:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來這兒玩的\N{\fs38}Oh, wow, man, I came here to have fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.28,0:08:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是現在我眼前一片憤怒的血紅\N{\fs38}and now I'm just seeing red.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者說 我能想象出的紅色\N{\fs38}Or at least my idea of what red is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 愛你 Chaz  - 加油啊 Chaz\N{\fs38}- Love you, Chaz! - Way to go, Chaz!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇哦 哇哦 哇哦 不用的 Mike\N{\fs38}Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa! Take it easy, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.48,0:08:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有球童的\N{\fs38}We got a caddy for that.
