Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.65,0:09:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們起了個壞頭\N{\fs38}with the whole incest thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.46,0:09:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許我的朋友 Jackson總統\N{\fs38}Maybe my friend, President Jackson,
