Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能幫我們解決這個問題\N{\fs38}can help ease out the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.94,0:09:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有見過他的雙胞胎弟弟\N{\fs38}And have you met his twin brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二任期的總統Jackson嗎\N{\fs38}second term President Jackson?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 幫不了你們\N{\fs38}Sorry, can't help you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.28,0:09:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了\N{\fs38}I see what's going on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.28,0:09:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一回家 你就等著上Yelp吧\N{\fs38}The second I get home, you're getting Yelped!
