Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.79,0:09:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在落后三竿感覺怎么樣\N{\fs38}How does it feel to be three strokes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是落后給法律承認的盲人\N{\fs38}behind a man who's legally blind?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法律承認\N{\fs38}"Legally blind"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 你是說 法律承認的盲人么\N{\fs38}Wait a minute, did you say "Legally blind"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.26,0:10:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話什么意思 你能看到大概的形狀嗎\N{\fs38}What does that mean? Can you see shapes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.72,0:10:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 你看得到形狀嗎\N{\fs38}I don't know. Can you see shapes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人看到嗎\N{\fs38}Nobody saw that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然沒人看到 真不敢相信\N{\fs38}Nobody saw that? Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.43,0:10:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人看到\N{\fs38}Nobody saw that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天\N{\fs38}Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 加油 chaz  - 你可以的\N{\fs38}- Come on, Chaz. - You can make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,0:10:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fs38}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 Chaz\N{\fs38}Come on, Chaz.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.41,0:10:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啊 小破孩\N{\fs38}Come on, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.63,0:10:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽爸爸們 幫幫忙管好你家孩子 行不\N{\fs38}Mom, dad, help us out here, will you please?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是豈有此理\N{\fs38}For crying out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該我了\N{\fs38}My turn.
