Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.95,0:10:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 接下來把桿B插進襯套Q里\N{\fs38}Okay, so just put pole "B" Into grommet "Q."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣應該差不多了\N{\fs38}And that should be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.09,0:10:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有旅館同意讓我們住 所以我們買了個帳篷花了200塊\N{\fs38}No hotel would take us, so we bought a tent for $200.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得賣我們帳篷的家伙敲了我們的竹杠\N{\fs38}I think the guy who sold it to us ripped us off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 他肯定是把我們兩個當情侶了\N{\fs38}Yeah, and he definitely thought we were a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像我們散發出了搞在一塊兒的感覺似的\N{\fs38}What, are we giving off some sort of chemistry vibe?
