Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.98,0:10:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也挺不錯的\N{\fs38}This isn't so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:10:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們大賺一筆\N{\fs38}We're making a tasty profit,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.57,0:10:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能在這兒享受下大自然\N{\fs38}and we're out here enjoying nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.77,0:11:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就是雙贏\N{\fs38}It's a win-win.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要\N{\fs38}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒放點東西進去壓著帳篷嗎\N{\fs38}You didn't put anything in there to weigh it down?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.38,0:11:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 只放了我的錢包進去 媽的 噢\N{\fs38}No, just my wallet. Damn it! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.07,0:11:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了別說了 我們趕緊走吧\N{\fs38}You know what, let's just get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.02,0:11:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有搞錯\N{\fs38}Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.48,0:11:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 拜托\N{\fs38}Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.79,0:11:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 這讓我想起來以前\N{\fs38}Oh, this reminds me when I used to
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小的時候玩過家家\N{\fs38}throw tea parties as a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把洋娃娃扮作客人\N{\fs38}My dolls would be the guests,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我讓Mike做服務員\N{\fs38}and I'd make Mike be the waiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷 是的 真不錯\N{\fs38}Cool. Yeah. Totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.74,0:11:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底有沒有在聽 Graham\N{\fs38}Are you even listening, Graham?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.53,0:11:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了 恩\N{\fs38}Totally. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.52,0:11:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來跟我8歲的小外甥約會\N{\fs38}Turns out going on a date with my eight-year-old nephew
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.65,0:11:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟其他男人約會沒什么兩樣\N{\fs38}is just like going on a date with any other guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我來晚了 但是有所收獲哦\N{\fs38}I'm sorry I'm late, but it wasn't all for naught.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我贏了這個\N{\fs38}I got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 這么說來你贏了  - 沒有\N{\fs38}- So you won. - Oh, God, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是參與獎\N{\fs38}That's a participation trophy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第二十三名\N{\fs38}No, I came in 23rd.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是Chaz第二十五\N{\fs38}But Chaz came in 25th.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mike 我真不敢相信你毀了我們的周末\N{\fs38}Mike, I can't believe you ruined our weekend
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.41,0:12:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就為了爭這么一點兒\N{\fs38}all over some grudge match
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.52,0:12:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是跟一個人挺好的盲人\N{\fs38}with a perfectly nice blind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.54,0:12:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就說怎么聽見一個成人的聲音\N{\fs38}I thought I heard the voice of an adult
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.22,0:12:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小孩兒身高的位置傳出來\N{\fs38}coming from the height range of a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.56,0:12:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇\N{\fs38}Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你故意把那袋子推翻\N{\fs38}You deliberately knocked over that bag,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.31,0:12:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我打偏那桿 你個作弊小人\N{\fs38}so I'd miss that putt, you cheater.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 我老公才不會作弊\N{\fs38}Hey, my husband is not a cheater.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.18,0:12:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 還是不是 這些都不重要\N{\fs38}"Is," "Isn't..." It's not important.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正重要的是我們要吃頓浪漫晚餐\N{\fs38}What is important is that we have that romantic dinner
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.78,0:12:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們說好的 我現在就開始想客房服務了\N{\fs38}we talked about-- I'm thinking room service.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲開晚宴 是吧\N{\fs38}Skipping the banquet, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.98,0:12:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己都覺得自己在宴會上丟人吧\N{\fs38}Figured you'd be too ashamed to show your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇哦 這人我真是看走眼了\N{\fs38}Wow, was I wrong about that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.11,0:12:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個混蛋 竟然說你作弊\N{\fs38}What a jerk. And to call you a cheater?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.22,0:12:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個瘋子 對吧\N{\fs38}Crazy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥 至少這事兒到此為止了\N{\fs38}Well, at least that story's over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.35,0:12:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃意大利菜 你呢\N{\fs38}I'm feeling Italian. How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.57,0:12:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 去他的浪漫\N{\fs38}No, screw romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.56,0:12:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就是要參加那個晚宴\N{\fs38}We are going to that banquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.26,0:12:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去斐濟玩怎么樣 我請客\N{\fs38}How about Fiji? My treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.44,0:12:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶貝兒 我們可以不用來的\N{\fs38}Honey, we don't have to do this.
