Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.40,0:12:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我們家窗戶就能看見那爛海\N{\fs38}We can see that garbage ocean from our apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.66,0:12:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來這兒是要贏回一局的\N{\fs38}We're here to settle a score.
