Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我謹代表新聞四臺\N{\fs38}On behalf of Channel Four News, thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.92,0:13:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝各位來支持圣阿比蓋爾醫院\N{\fs38}for coming out to support the research wing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.87,0:13:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究翼樓的建設\N{\fs38}of St. Abigail's Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.17,0:13:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我們募集到超過1500元\N{\fs38}And today we raised over $1,500--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.61,0:13:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 沒錯吧\N{\fs38}What? Was that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fs38}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛得知我們要改為\N{\fs38}Well, I've been told we're switching
