Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs36}cash bar 來賓需自己花錢買酒open bar 酒由主辦方出資提供
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請各位享用晚餐吧\N{\fs38}Enjoy your meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話 我想要說幾句話\N{\fs38}I'd like to say a few words if I may.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心 我不會把你的晚餐騙走的\N{\fs38}Don't worry, I won't cheat you out of your dinners.
