Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.34,0:13:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作弊 -- 不論是在高爾夫球\N{\fs38}cheating-- whether it be at golf
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是生活的其他方面 -- 都是可恥的\N{\fs38}or any of life's endeavors-- is truly despicable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.97,0:13:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論如何 來到這里都是一種榮幸\N{\fs38}Anyways, it's an honor to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個非常偉大的事業 請盡情享用晚餐\N{\fs38}This is a great, great cause. And enjoy your meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.23,0:13:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快說點什么呀\N{\fs38}Say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能來到這里實在是榮幸之極\N{\fs38}I too am honored to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.96,0:14:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給圣Abigail醫院捐款\N{\fs38}Giving to St. Abigail's is
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.28,0:14:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如同在給未來做投資\N{\fs38}like an investment in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.02,0:14:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都知道 我們的孩子才是未來\N{\fs38}And we all know that our children are the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.27,0:14:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如這個男孩兒\N{\fs38}Like this boy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂得保持低調\N{\fs38}The kind of kid who knows to keep his head down
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.63,0:14:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不多說話\N{\fs38}and not say too much and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.65,0:14:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道分寸\N{\fs38}know his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次重申 這是個非常 非常 非常\N{\fs38}So once again, it's a great, great, great,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.47,0:14:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常 非常 非常 偉大的事業\N{\fs38}great, great, great, great cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們別把它搞砸了\N{\fs38}And let's not do anything to screw it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.41,0:14:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請享用晚餐吧\N{\fs38}Enjoy the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.16,0:14:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 就這么點  - 是的 就這樣吧\N{\fs38}- That's it? - Yeah, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 我是Annie Henry  Mike的妻子\N{\fs38}Hi. Annie Henry, Mike's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.70,0:14:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很榮幸\N{\fs38}Also honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.71,0:14:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這位廣告曲作家\N{\fs38}I think that the jingle writer
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.67,0:14:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關于作弊說的話非常對\N{\fs38}made a good point about cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.03,0:14:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一點是 如果我們不支持\N{\fs38}Another point-- if we don't support
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.37,0:14:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣Abigail醫院 難道我們就都是輸家嗎\N{\fs38}St. Abigail's, aren't we all losers?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我們中有些人 是輸不起\N{\fs38}Maybe some of us, sore losers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有比這種輸不起的人\N{\fs38}And is there anything worse
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.52,0:14:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更糟的嗎\N{\fs38}than a sore loser?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.90,0:14:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了這個研究試圖\N{\fs38}Other than the diseases that this research
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.78,0:14:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要治愈的疾病之外\N{\fs38}is trying to cure?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.56,0:15:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個 好 很好 非常好 真是\N{\fs38}This is a great, great, super great, really,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.35,0:15:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堪稱最好的事業了\N{\fs38}just the best cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.32,0:15:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請享用各位的晚餐\N{\fs38}Enjoy your meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.95,0:15:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能不能再來一杯果汁\N{\fs38}Can I get some more juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這已經是第五杯了\N{\fs38}That was your fifth glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.37,0:15:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喝得夠多了\N{\fs38}Maybe you've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回家也能喝的\N{\fs38}I could get this at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.91,0:15:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樓上有蘋果汁的\N{\fs38}We have apple juice upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.74,0:15:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聲拍賣正式結束\N{\fs38}And the silent auction is now officially closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.74,0:15:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs36}主辦方在桌子上放置拍賣單，競拍者只需在物品下填寫出價即可
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.07,0:15:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很驕傲的宣布 我們籌集到了\N{\fs38}I'm proud to announce that we have raised...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.67,0:15:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,250美元\N{\fs38}$250?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.36,0:15:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是夠了\N{\fs38}All right. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.38,0:15:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把巧克力噴泉關掉\N{\fs38}Turn off the chocolate fountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.02,0:15:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不加番茄醬\N{\fs38}If you're not gonna use the ketchup,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就別把瓶子打開\N{\fs38}don't open the bottles just for the hell of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害啊 Henry\N{\fs38}Real nice, Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.99,0:15:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你的老婆幫你打嘴仗\N{\fs38}Getting your wife to fight your battles for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.18,0:15:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得承認她很厲害\N{\fs38}Well, you have to admit she's good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.77,0:15:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對一個法律承認的盲人作弊了\N{\fs38}Hey, hey, you cheated against a legally blind man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.58,0:15:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法律承認\N{\fs38}Legally blind?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mike 他能看見形狀\N{\fs38}Mike, this guy can see shapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.67,0:15:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在說這事兒\N{\fs38}That's what I've been saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可笑 閃開\N{\fs38}Okay, this is ridiculous. Out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.88,0:15:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道Mike站那兒的\N{\fs38}Hey, how did you know where Mike was?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.55,0:15:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非\N{\fs38}Unless...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著\N{\fs38}Think fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.76,0:16:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這什么也證明不了\N{\fs38}Well, that didn't prove anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.53,0:16:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這就走\N{\fs38}We'll show ourselves out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.58,0:16:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拿龍蝦砸了一個盲人 一下子\N{\fs38}You hit one blind dude with a lobster, and then, oh, suddenly,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.90,0:16:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你就成了壞人了  - 我明白\N{\fs38}- you're the bad guy. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們才是受害者\N{\fs38}We're the victims here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.32,0:16:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 看\N{\fs38}Oh, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.53,0:16:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吶 看吶\N{\fs38}Lookee, lookee.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海景套房\N{\fs38}Ocean view suite.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門大開著\N{\fs38}Wide open.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.07,0:16:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們說都訂滿了\N{\fs38}They said it was all full.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這本來是屬于我們的海景\N{\fs38}That was supposed to be our view.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.79,0:16:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進去看看也無傷大雅吧\N{\fs38}Well, it wouldn't hurt to take a little peek.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 大海\N{\fs38}Yep, that's an ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.46,0:16:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來 試試從這邊看怎么樣\N{\fs38}Come and see what it looks like from over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那邊要遠一些啊\N{\fs38}But that's further away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 我懂了\N{\fs38}Oh, I see what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:17:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒開玩笑吧 干嘛鎖上\N{\fs38}Ugh, are you serious? Why would you lock this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.40,0:17:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不讓別人像我們這樣進去啊\N{\fs38}So that people like us can't get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得好\N{\fs38}Solid point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.82,0:17:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是史上最爛的一夜\N{\fs38}Worst night ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我們的下場\N{\fs38}This is what we get.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽和爸爸那么信任我們\N{\fs38}Mom and dad put a roof over our head,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我們卻在背后捅他們刀子  - 過了這么一天\N{\fs38}- and we stab them in the back.  - After the day we've had,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.65,0:17:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以后一定會尊重爸媽\N{\fs38}I am never disrespecting mom and dad again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我才不要像一只鴿子一樣\N{\fs38}All right, well, I'm not sleeping
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.08,0:17:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡在外面\N{\fs38}out here like a pigeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把鎖撬開\N{\fs38}I am gonna jimmy open that lock
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個腰帶\N{\fs38}with this belt--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fs38}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要八十美元呢 這樣我們賺的錢就都沒了\N{\fs38}Oh, that was $80. Now we're not making any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要把我的那份也花在你的破腰帶上\N{\fs38}I'm not paying for your cheesy belt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.11,0:17:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是阿瑪尼休閑 你真是沒有時尚感\N{\fs38}It was Armani Exchange! You have no sense of fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.97,0:17:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你在逗我嗎  - 一點都沒有\N{\fs38}- Are you serious? - Just zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的\N{\fs38}Honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這有對無家可歸的小兩口\N{\fs38}There's a homeless couple
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.29,0:17:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在防火梯上吵架呢\N{\fs38}having a lovers' quarrel on the fire escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.47,0:17:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 不 我們住這兒  - 我們也不是小兩口\N{\fs38}- No, we live here. - And we're not a couple!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事\N{\fs38}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們說實話吧\N{\fs38}Let's just tell them the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fs38}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.60,0:17:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的父母這周末把公寓租了出去\N{\fs38}Our parents rented out the apartment for the weekend
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.44,0:17:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒地方去了\N{\fs38}and left us with nowhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 可憐的孩子\N{\fs38}Oh, you poor things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.47,0:17:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太過分了\N{\fs38}That's awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來吧 我給你們拿攤子\N{\fs38}Come in. We'll get you some blankets.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的 幫幫我\N{\fs38}Honey, help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.31,0:17:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說好的不給爸媽背后捅刀呢\N{\fs38}What ever happened to not betraying mom and dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.08,0:17:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我好冷  - 好吧\N{\fs38}- I was cold. - Yeah. Ooh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:17:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身材保持的真好\N{\fs38}Stay in form. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你\N{\fs38}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.68,0:18:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發誓我讓門開著\N{\fs38}I could have sworn I left it open,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好讓我能再找到的\N{\fs38}so I could find it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.57,0:18:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是盲人嘛\N{\fs38}You know, 'cause I'm blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.84,0:18:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎\N{\fs38}Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.66,0:18:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下也別動\N{\fs38}Keep perfectly still.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道你在和誰說話對吧\N{\fs38}You know who you're talking to, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.85,0:18:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的沒錯 我能看見形狀\N{\fs38}You were right. I can see shapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇哦\N{\fs38}Skiddily wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.04,0:18:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 噢  - 就是這個人栽贓我\N{\fs38}- Oh.  - That's the guy who blamed me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄翻了高爾夫球袋\N{\fs38}for knocking over the golf bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我站起來說了你那么多好話\N{\fs38}And after all the nice things I said about you in my speech...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋\N{\fs38}Son of a--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.48,0:18:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你陷害了一個十歲小孩兒\N{\fs38}So you framed a ten-year-old kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.53,0:18:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫不為此驕傲\N{\fs38}Not my proudest moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.68,0:18:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天到底是怎么了\N{\fs38}What happened today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.39,0:18:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般來說 你只是為了玩得開心\N{\fs38}Usually, you're just happy to have fun out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.67,0:18:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打高爾夫不會這么好勝的\N{\fs38}It's not like you to be so competitive about golf.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.39,0:18:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是高爾夫的問題\N{\fs38}Oh, it wasn't about the golf.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.42,0:19:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想要塑造勵志形象而已\N{\fs38}I just want to be the inspirational guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.63,0:19:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想這已經在我的身份里\N{\fs38}I mean, I guess it's become
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占據了比我意識到的還要多的位置\N{\fs38}a bigger part of my identity than I realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.78,0:19:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這么說能讓你好受點\N{\fs38}If it makes you feel any better,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對于真正了解你的人來說\N{\fs38}to the people who really know you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.89,0:19:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你并不是很勵志啊\N{\fs38}you're not all that inspiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.64,0:19:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 完全沒讓我好受點  - 我只是說 \N{\fs38}- Doesn't help.  - I'm just saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.91,0:19:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對孩子們來說 你是個親切的爸爸\N{\fs38}To the kids, you're an embarrassing dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.39,0:19:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說 你是靈魂伴侶兼搶被子的\N{\fs38}To me, you're a soul mate/blanket hog.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對現實吧 對那個純潔的十歲小孩\N{\fs38}And let's face it, to that innocent ten-year-old boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.48,0:19:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不過是一個大騙子\N{\fs38}you are nothing but a big, fat cheater.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"純潔" 他看著就賊眉鼠眼的\N{\fs38}"Innocent"? He had shifty eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.51,0:19:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往好的方面想\N{\fs38}On the bright side,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.59,0:19:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我們不會再被邀請\N{\fs38}I don't think we'll be invited
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.26,0:19:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去任何周末高爾夫活動了\N{\fs38}to any more golf weekends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.83,0:19:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這都是你的秘密計劃的一部分\N{\fs38}So this was all part of your secret plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.03,0:19:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想待在\N{\fs38}I'm just glad to be somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.58,0:19:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不會被人說三道四的地方\N{\fs38}where we won't be judged.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.38,0:19:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼\N{\fs38}Well, well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.77,0:19:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果來的不是史上最差父母\N{\fs38}If it isn't the worst parents ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.02,0:19:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倆該進監獄\N{\fs38}You two should be in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.43,0:19:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們回來早了啊\N{\fs38}You're home early.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.45,0:19:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些人是誰 這些小孩是誰\N{\fs38}Who are these people? Who are these children?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.93,0:19:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 啊  - 電影時間\N{\fs38}- Ah!  - Movie time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.27,0:19:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看什么 <火爆群龍> 還是 <野鴨變鳳凰>\N{\fs38}What's it gonna be, Slap Shot or Mighty Ducks?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 兩部冰球電影 就只能選這些\N{\fs38}Seriously, two hockey movies? Those are my choices?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.82,0:20:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被禁足了就是這樣\N{\fs38}That's what happens when you're grounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.41,0:20:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 但是 媽  - 再廢話\N{\fs38}- But, mom...  - Keep it up,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就看兩部\N{\fs38}and you watch both.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.41,0:20:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的處境很危險哦\N{\fs38}You're on thin ice. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.74,0:20:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候 你得習慣扮演某個角色\N{\fs38}Sometimes, you get used to playing certain roles.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.78,0:20:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破冰者 嘿 伙計\N{\fs38}Icebreaker, hey, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.91,0:20:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許是雄心壯志的\N{\fs38}Maybe you're the ambitious one
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.78,0:20:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聰明的 或是 勵志的\N{\fs38}or the smart one or the inspiring one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.78,0:20:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上回來\N{\fs38}I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.39,0:20:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你不能讓\N{\fs38}- - But you can't let
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.09,0:20:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些角色擺布你  - 你好\N{\fs38}- those roles define you.  - Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 嘿 Leigh姑姑  - 是你啊\N{\fs38}- Hey, Aunt Leigh.  - Oh. It's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨\N{\fs38}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要來看電影嗎\N{\fs38}Want to come watch a movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就去\N{\fs38}I'll be right up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.91,0:20:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他第二天打電話來了\N{\fs38}He called the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦\N{\fs38}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.77,0:20:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你太在意他人的看法\N{\fs38}Because if you're too caught up in how other people see you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.16,0:20:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可能會忘了要停下來欣賞風景\N{\fs38}you might forget to stop and enjoy the view.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.13,0:20:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這比斐濟島更好\N{\fs38}You know, I think this is better than Fiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.19,0:20:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的月亮 我是海龜\N{\fs38}Well, you are my moon, and I am the sea turtle
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.15,0:20:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爬過波利尼西亞的熱沙灘\N{\fs38}paddling across the hot Polynesian sands--
